                "invention-title": [
                    "Low-carbon operation method based on oxygen-enriched combuste-P2G and gradient stepped carbon transaction mechanism",
                    "基于富氧燃烧-P2G与递变阶梯碳交易机制的低碳运行方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a low-carbon operation method based on oxygen-enriched combuste-P2G and a gradient stepped carbon transaction mechanism, and the method comprises the steps: 1, introducing an oxygen-enriched combustion model and a power-to-gas model into a comprehensive energy system, researching an oxygen-enriched combustion-power-to-gas coupled working mechanism, and carrying out the modeling of an oxygen-enriched combustion-power-to-gas combined operation mode; 2, introducing a gradient stepped carbon transaction mechanism into the integrated energy system, and constructing a gradient stepped carbon transaction mechanism model; 3, according to the actual operation condition of the comprehensive energy system, operation models of energy conversion equipment and energy storage equipment of the comprehensive energy system are established, and a multi-energy-flow balance equation of electricity, heat, gas and hydrogen is listed; 4, constructing a low-carbon economic operation target with the minimum total operation cost of the system, and calling a CPLEX solver to solve and analyze different set scenes; the wind power absorption space can be effectively expanded, the economical efficiency of the system is improved, and the carbon emission level is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种基于富氧燃烧‑P2G与递变阶梯碳交易机制的低碳运行方法，包括步骤1：分别将富氧燃烧模型与电转气模型引入到综合能源系统，研究富氧燃烧‑电转气耦合的工作机理以及对富氧燃烧‑电转气联合运行模式进行建模；步骤2：将递变阶梯碳交易机制引入到综合能源系统，并构建递变阶梯碳交易机制模型；步骤3：根据综合能源系统的实际运行情况，建立综合能源系统的能量转化设备和能量存储设备的运行模型，列写电、热、气、氢的多能流平衡方程；步骤4：构建以系统总运行成本最小的低碳经济运行目标，并调用CPLEX求解器对设置的不同场景进行求解分析；本发明能够有效拓展风电消纳空间，提高系统的经济性以及降低碳排放水平。"
                }
            ]
